            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class=" py-2">
                    <p class="mt-4 bg-white p-3" id="losinfo"><i class="fa fa-walking" style="color:blue;"></i> Exercises:  <span id="losinfo">Your program weekly progress.</span></p>
                    <small>Week 1</small>
